00:38:56,001 --> 00:38:58,640
Gostevsky is going to hit you over the head with it when the time comes.

445
00:38:58,641 --> 00:39:01,521
But it starts on 179.

446
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,601
Here's what Zosima does.

447
00:39:03,601 --> 00:39:19,361
