448
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,800
Some confessed kneeling.

449
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:26,561
The elder absolved, reconciled, exhorted, imposed penance, blessed and dismissed them.

450
00:39:26,561 --> 00:39:35,681
It was against this general confession that the opponents of elders protested, maintaining that it profaned the sacrament of confession.

451
00:39:35,681 --> 00:39:36,720
Well, it does.

